    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="IguanaTex"><a href="#IguanaTex" class="headerlink" title="IguanaTex"></a>IguanaTex</h2><p>IguanaTex是一款方便的powerpoint公式编辑插件。<br><a href="http://www.jonathanleroux.org/software/iguanatex/" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">下载地址</a><br>下载安装后，会出现在powerpoint的菜单栏上<br><img src="/2018/12/28/pptlatex/iguanatex.jpg" alt="iguanatex"></p><p>IguanaTex可以非常方便的与mathtype配合，在ppt中输入公式：<br>首先在mathtype的preference选项中，选择cut and copy preferences为mathml or Tex:<br><img src="/2018/12/28/pptlatex/mathtype.jpg" alt="mathtype preference"></p><p>之后在mathtype中编辑任何一个公式，例如：<br><img src="/2018/12/28/pptlatex/equations.jpg" alt="equations"></p><p>将这些公式全选复制，然后在ppt的Iguanatex菜单栏选择new Latex display,出现如下对话框:<br><img src="/2018/12/28/pptlatex/newequation.jpg" alt="newequations"></p><p>将复制的latex公式填入到对话框<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\[\begin&#123;array&#125;&#123;l&#125;</span><br><span class="line">x = \sqrt &#123;&#123;b^2&#125; - 4ac&#125; \\</span><br><span class="line">y = \frac&#123;&#123; - b \pm \sqrt &#123;&#123;b^2&#125; - 4ac&#125; &#125;&#125;&#123;&#123;2a&#125;&#125;\\</span><br><span class="line">z = \frac&#123;&#123;n!&#125;&#125;&#123;&#123;r!\left( &#123;n - r&#125; \right)!&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">\end&#123;array&#125;\]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>之后界面如图:<br><img src="/2018/12/28/pptlatex/afterpaste.jpg" alt="afterpaste"><br>点击generate之后，在ppt中生成公式：</p><p><img src="/2018/12/28/pptlatex/generate.jpg" alt="generate"></p><h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><blockquote><ul><li><a href="http://www.jonathanleroux.org/software/iguanatex/" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Iguanatex主页：http://www.jonathanleroux.org/software/iguanatex/</a></li></ul></blockquote>]]></content>
    
