    <title>在hexo主页中添加百度分享</title>
    <link href="https://yongcaiwang.github.io/2018/12/26/hexoshare/"/>
    <id>https://yongcaiwang.github.io/2018/12/26/hexoshare/</id>
    <published>2018-12-26T01:10:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-12-26T01:31:48.323Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="在hexo中使用wikitten模板时添加百度分享的方法。"><a href="#在hexo中使用wikitten模板时添加百度分享的方法。" class="headerlink" title="在hexo中使用wikitten模板时添加百度分享的方法。"></a>在hexo中使用wikitten模板时添加百度分享的方法。</h2><p>网上查找在hexo中添加链接分享的方法是，查到的都是用next主题的，<br>用wikitten主题时，如何添加分享并没有介绍。</p><p>自己翻了一下代码，发现wikitten主题的结构非常清楚。</p><ul><li>首先，在_config.xml中的share选项中的几个分享的选项</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Share</span></span><br><span class="line">share: bdshare <span class="comment"># options: jiathis, bdshare, addtoany, default</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在\themes\Wikitten\layout\share文件夹中都有对应的文件。<br><img src="/2018/12/26/hexoshare/sharelist.jpg" alt="share文件夹中的文件"></p><p>打开bdshare.ejs 可以把现在已经不存在的开心网，腾讯微博的链接去掉，只保留qq空间，新浪微博和微信<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div class=<span class="string">"bdsharebuttonbox"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"bds_more"</span> data-cmd=<span class="string">"more"</span>&gt;  分享到：&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"bds_qzone"</span> data-cmd=<span class="string">"qzone"</span> title=<span class="string">"分享到QQ空间"</span>&gt;QQ空间&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"bds_tsina"</span> data-cmd=<span class="string">"tsina"</span> title=<span class="string">"分享到新浪微博"</span>&gt;新浪微博&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"bds_weixin"</span> data-cmd=<span class="string">"weixin"</span> title=<span class="string">"分享到微信"</span>&gt;微信&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>之后把保存的bdshare.ejs放到\themes\Wikitten\layout\common目录下</p><p>修改common目录下的article.ejs。article.ejs就是决定着hexo生成的静态文件的布局。<br>我们可以把分享链接放到文章的标题栏的日期的位置<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div class=<span class="string">"article-meta"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'post/category'</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'post/tag'</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'post/date'</span>, &#123; class_name: <span class="string">'article-date'</span>, date_format: null &#125;) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'share/bdshare'</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.plugins.busuanzi_count) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;i class=<span class="string">"fa fa-bar-chart"</span>&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;span id=<span class="string">"busuanzi_container_site_pv"</span>&gt;&lt;span id=<span class="string">"busuanzi_value_page_pv"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;    </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.history_control.enable) &#123; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">let</span> repertory_address = `<span class="variable">$&#123;theme.history_control.server_link&#125;</span>/<span class="variable">$&#123;theme.history_control.user&#125;</span>/<span class="variable">$&#123;theme.history_control.repertory&#125;</span>`;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">let</span> file_path = `<span class="variable">$&#123;theme.history_control.branch&#125;</span>/<span class="built_in">source</span>/<span class="variable">$&#123;post.source&#125;</span>`;%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=<span class="string">"article-meta-button"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a href=<span class="string">'&lt;%= `$&#123;repertory_address&#125;/raw/$&#123;file_path&#125;` %&gt;'</span>&gt; Source &lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=<span class="string">"article-meta-button"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a href=<span class="string">'&lt;%= `$&#123;repertory_address&#125;/edit/$&#123;file_path&#125;` %&gt;'</span>&gt; Edit &lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=<span class="string">"article-meta-button"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a href=<span class="string">'&lt;%= `$&#123;repertory_address&#125;/commits/$&#123;file_path&#125;` %&gt;'</span>&gt; History &lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>如上述的代码，把<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'share/bdshare'</span>) %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>放到了<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%- partial(<span class="string">'post/date'</span>, &#123; class_name: <span class="string">'article-date'</span>, date_format: null &#125;) %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>的后面。</p><p>这样，在每个页面中就可以看到百度分享的链接:<br><img src="/2018/12/26/hexoshare/baidusharefig.jpg" alt="share文件夹中的文件"></p><h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><blockquote><ul><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wizardforcel/article/details/40707993" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">ApacheCN_飞龙的CSDN博客，但是不完全一样</a></li><li><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/a1169877388c" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">PigPeek的简书博客，也不太一样</a></li></ul></blockquote>]]></content>
    
